Base project containing all my settings for both Linux and MacOS systems.
On a freshly installed sytem, clone this repo to $HOME:

$ git clone git@github.com:elf-alchemist/dotfiles.git ~/dotfiles
$ cd ~/dotfiles


Symlink the respective directories, as per the following:

$ ln -sfn ~/dotfiles/config ~/.config
$ ln -sfn ~/dotfiles/local  ~/.local


Now, let's the stubborn ones that do not conform to the XDG standard.

$ ln -sfn ~/dotfiles/config/ssh      ~/.ssh            
$ ln -sfn ~/dotfiles/config/irssi    ~/.irssi
$ ln -sfn ~/dotfiles/local/share/pki ~/.pki
$ ln -sfn ~/dotfiles/bashrc          ~/.bashrc
$ ln -sfn ~/dotfiles/bashrc          ~/.bash_profile

